{"tid":1665244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要connect 伊斯蘭教絕對唔只清潔咁簡單","createTime":"2019-10-20T13:43:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T09:37:07.000Z","uid":84408,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"67624ed07ae80f23195aa3b0dcaeb01891bf72f7","tid":1665244,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T13:43:34.000Z","msg":"眾所周知 香港地申請難民係難到仆街<br />\n酷刑聲請絕對唔係想像中咁易<br />\n基本上新移民一個月黎嘅量已經多過難民嘅數量<br />\n所以香港地好多南亞手足都係土生土長 只係融入唔到咁解<br />\n要connect 佢地真係要比機會佢地融入香港嘅文化<br />\n互相尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為佢地今次幫我地出聲stand with Hong Kong 有機會導致佢地日後受班狗刁難<br />\n希望香港人呢個身份認同可以再創高峰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b5285ff6870c32b49f0a263cb0b7c659ccc724","tid":1665244,"uid":266279,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T13:44:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DD8_tEWp9Ts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDD8_tEWp9Ts&d=g2FbBnZIPvId2LkE7nNtjS9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=5accadf1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DD8_tEWp9Ts</a><br />\n清真寺民眾Philip Khan怒斥香港政府侮辱伊斯蘭教 <br />\n推爆國際字幕版Twitter:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HongKongNewsTV5/status/1185874822384930822?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHongKongNewsTV5%2Fstatus%2F1185874822384930822%3Fs%3D20&d=g2FbBnZIPvId2LkE7nNtjS9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=6df3d8f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHongKongNewsTV5%2Fstatus%2F1185874822384930822%3Fs%3D20&h=85a8ab0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HongKongNewsTV5/status/1185874822384930822?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"3d0d73ef550e9f1658b37c372ba1fde45e614088","tid":1665244,"uid":84408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T13:47:03.000Z","msg":"btw 班pprb道個歉就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji